{"tid":1838163,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩發現左個方法令街上啲廢老戴口罩","createTime":"2020-01-24T02:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T16:33:54.000Z","uid":82312,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6e52df36e893455a967753998dbce78f7397d6bd","tid":1838163,"uid":82312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T02:20:42.000Z","msg":"岩岩排隊塔巴士一半人唔戴口罩<br />\n目測一係大陸人一係藍絲自私廢老<br />\n因為我有鼻敏感一早一晚會打黑痴<br />\n唔覺意打左下 然後我見前後啲人縮一縮<br />\n靈機一觸我起勢力打多幾下<br />\n嘩 一分鍾內一個二個係個袋到拎返個口罩戴<br />\n嘩屌 原黎班仆街自己都有準備口罩但唔戴<br />\n真係奶野班仆街都奶晒啦<br />\n大家可以試下<br />\n我地戴晒口罩都不及班廢老大陸人病原體戴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4969401bb7fe63d65734f56b988ebe51f13e1d1","tid":1838163,"uid":77102,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T02:35:30.000Z","msg":"但係乞痴好似唔關肺炎事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ed62e7d804cfb57f513d2a4f4315825590f7d1","tid":1838163,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T02:36:25.000Z","msg":"「突發」四個醫療工會不排除於初四後發起工業行動！(終極整合）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837445</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8e2a9062296a116e2801b58a28b536600adc55bf","tid":1838163,"uid":203685,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"a4969401bb7fe63d65734f56b988ebe51f13e1d1","tid":1838163,"uid":77102,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T02:35:30.000Z","msg":"但係乞痴好似唔關肺炎事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T02:38:46.000Z","msg":"但d廢老on9架"},{"pid":"b9f252c372abd285dfafb97803059c62f96d214a","tid":1838163,"uid":77102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8e2a9062296a116e2801b58a28b536600adc55bf","tid":1838163,"uid":203685,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"a4969401bb7fe63d65734f56b988ebe51f13e1d1","tid":1838163,"uid":77102,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score